idl_bin instructions

All needed to run the application are the files specified in the config file
idl_bin.cfg 

> idl -vm='idl_bin.sav'

Make sure the idl_bin.cfg file is edited first. In this configuration file,
it is possible to define a set of runs.
	Example:
		<number>1,3,5-10,13,14,15</number>
	will run idl_bin for the following runs
		1,3,5,6,7,8,9,10,13,14 and 15
		
		







